### âœ§ Echo Return (Response of Space)

```
Echo / Architectural Feedback
ð„ž  |    (rest)   C~   (tie)  E~  |
                 p          pp
```

* Enters **one beat late**
* Softer (p â†’ pp)
* Tied notes indicate **blur, not intent**
* Pitch-matched: *confirmation*, not argument

---

### âœ§ Second Harmonic Bloom (Cathedral Effect)

```
Echo Harmonics
ð„ž  |        G~       (fade)        |
                  ppp
```

* Only the fifth survives
* Indicates **selective reinforcement**
* This is where *awe* lives

