## III. Mapping Directly Back to the Equation

This notation corresponds exactly to:

[
E_a = \int_0^{T_{60}} \mathcal{E}(t),dt
]

* The **echo staff is ( \mathcal{E}(t) )**
* Dynamic decay = ( e^{-\lambda t} )
* Delay = ( \tau )
* Î¼ gate is enforced by:

  * slow tempo
  * no rhythmic acceleration
  * no lyrical content in echo

