## IV. Why This Is So Powerful (Visually)

Even on the page:

* You **see** that no one is shouting
* You **see** that the room answers, not commands
* You **see** time being stretched safely
* You **see** containment

This is why:

* choirs calm courts
* chants regulate crowds
* cathedrals prevent panic
* and rallies without echo go feral

